{"id": "onzeker-groeitempo-retail-door-geopolitieke-instabiliteit__c4-paragraph__0004", "text": "In 2025, we expect a slight volume growth of 1 percent for retail, partly due to a recovery in purchasing power. However, the growth rate remains uncertain due to external factors such as geopolitical instability. In this video, sector economist Gerarda Westerhuis explains in 2 minutes what challenges retail faces and what you can do as an entrepreneur.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "onzeker-groeitempo-retail-door-geopolitieke-instabiliteit__c4-paragraph__0004", "source_slug": "onzeker-groeitempo-retail-door-geopolitieke-instabiliteit", "source_title": "Uncertain retail growth rate due to geopolitical instability", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/retail/onzeker-groeitempo-retail-door-geopolitieke-instabiliteit.html", "source_date": "2025-08-15", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
