{"id": "onzeker-groeitempo-retail-door-geopolitieke-instabiliteit__c4-paragraph__0007", "text": "Growth varies between the different branches within the retail sector. Drugstores in particular are doing well, while furniture and consumer electronics stores are struggling to grow their sales volumes and turnover.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "onzeker-groeitempo-retail-door-geopolitieke-instabiliteit__c4-paragraph__0007", "source_slug": "onzeker-groeitempo-retail-door-geopolitieke-instabiliteit", "source_title": "Uncertain retail growth rate due to geopolitical instability", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/retail/onzeker-groeitempo-retail-door-geopolitieke-instabiliteit.html", "source_date": "2025-08-15", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 16, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
